íŸ@0a420ab7fa4f80ddd95c9070a6347cf7780b849e4a28bd35d1e97b402606a611ŸƒTitle: title: to yml
Path: Examples
Content:
Outputs a YAML string representing the contents of this table.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[foo bar]; ["1" "2"]] | to yml
- foo: '1'
  bar: '2'


```
